Pseudocode for Angel Investor:

set fund account to (starting amount)
print investment options
user input to choose investments
set turn to current turn
turn = days passed
user select time passage
random events stop time passage( i.e. war, strike, alien invasion, zombie epidemic)
new investment options become available (i.e. zombie serum maker)
random generation of business hurdles for each investment
each event has corresponding image displayed

win condition = account passes defined threshold
perhaps table/grid with status/info for each company
